						"description": "Translate text from source language to target language, then synthesize speech.\n\n**Translation parameters (optional):**\n- `src_lang`: Source language code (e.g., 'eng_Latn')\n- `tgt_lang`: Target language code (e.g., 'urd_Arab')\n\n**TTS parameters (required):**\n- `text`: Text to process\n- `language`: Target language for TTS (e.g., 'en', 'ur', 'hi')\n- `speaker_id`: User ID for voice cloning (default: 'default')\n\nIf `src_lang` and `tgt_lang` are provided, translation will be performed first, then TTS will be applied to the translated text."
